Package org.apache.juneau.reflect

Class AnnotationInfo<T extends java.lang.annotation.Annotation>

java.lang.Object
org.apache.juneau.reflect.AnnotationInfo<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The annotation type.
public final class AnnotationInfo<T extends java.lang.annotation.Annotation>
extends java.lang.Object
Represents an annotation instance on a class and the class it was found on.
